{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"特性簡寫","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"定義","title":"定義","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>特性簡寫，是一種可以同時設定許多其他 CSS 屬性值的 CSS 屬性。</em> 使用特性簡寫，網頁開發者可以寫出更簡潔、且通常更具可讀性的樣式表，省時又省力。</p>\n<p>CSS 規範中定義，特性簡寫用來組合作用於相同主題的常見性質。舉例來說，CSS <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background\"><code>background</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 這個性質是個特性簡寫，可同時定義 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-image\"><code>background-image</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-repeat\"><code>background-repeat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, 和 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-position\"><code>background-position</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 等屬性。同樣的，最常用的字體相關屬性，可以使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/font\"><code>font</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 來定義；圍繞在方塊周圍的邊界，則可簡單地以 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 簡寫來定義。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"需謹慎之處","title":"需謹慎之處","isH3":false,"content":"<p>即便特性簡寫非常易於使用，仍有幾個需要銘記在心的情況：</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>未指明的值會被設為預設值。這聽起來真的很怪，但他的確會<strong>覆寫</strong>先前的設定值。比如：\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>images/bg.gif<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> no-repeat top right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>不會將背景設為紅色，而是使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> 的預設值 <code>transparent</code>，由於較後面的規則為優先。\n  </li>\n  <li>只有獨立的屬性可以被繼承。就如同遺失的值會被預設值取代一樣，不可能讓缺漏的值再去繼承個別屬性。關鍵字 <code>inherit</code> 可以用於屬性，但只能整體繼承，而不能用於個別值上。意思是，如果要繼承某個特定的值，就必須使用完整的語句，搭配 <code>inherit</code> 關鍵字<code>。</code></li>\n  <li>簡寫屬性試著不強迫使用特定順序，在那些屬性有許多不同類型的值的狀況下的確很方便。但是在許多屬性具有類似值時就沒這麼簡單了，此時會以以下規則處理：\n    <ol>\n      <li>關於區塊的簡寫性質，諸如 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-style\"><code>border-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 或 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding\"><code>padding</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>，就會使用連貫的１～４個值來定義下列這些邊：\n        <table>\n          <thead>\n            <tr>\n              <th>\n                <img src=\"/files/3646/border1.png\" alt=\"border1.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </th>\n              <th><em>單值語法：</em><code>border-width: 1em</code> — 這個唯一的值定義所有四邊</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td>\n                <img src=\"/files/3647/border2.png\" alt=\"border2.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </td>\n              <td><em>雙值語法：</em><code>border-width: 1em 2em</code> — 第一個值代表垂直部分，也就是上和下邊；第二個值則是指水平部分，也就是左右邊。</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>\n                <img src=\"/files/3648/border3.png\" alt=\"border3.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </td>\n              <td><em>三值語法：</em><code>border-width: 1em 2em 3em</code> — 第一個值代表上邊，第二個值代表兩旁的邊，而第三個值代表下邊。</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>\n                <img src=\"/files/3649/border4.png\" alt=\"border4.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </td>\n              <td><em>四值語法：</em><code>border-width: 1em 2em 3em 4em</code> — 這四個值分別代表上、右、下、左邊，順時針的方向由上開始排列（可以以 trouble 來記憶，即英文首文字的縮寫 TRBL）</td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </li>\n      <li>與之相似地，關於區塊角落的屬性，像是 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-radius\"><code>border-radius</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>，也會使用連貫的１～４個值來代表四個角落：\n        <table>\n          <thead>\n            <tr>\n              <th>\n                <img src=\"/files/3650/corner1.png\" alt=\"corner1.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </th>\n              <th><em>單值語法：</em><code>border-radius: 1em</code> — 這唯一的值代表了所有角落。</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td>\n                <img src=\"/files/3651/corner2.png\" alt=\"corner2.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </td>\n              <td><em>雙值語法：</em><code>border-radius: 1em 2em</code> — 第一個值代表左上和右下，第二個值則是右上及左下角。</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>\n                <img src=\"/files/3652/corner3.png\" alt=\"corner3.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </td>\n              <td><em>三值語法：</em><code>border-radius: 1em 2em 3em</code> — 第一個值代表左上，第二個值代表右上及左下，第三個值則是右下的角落。</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td>\n                <img src=\"/files/3653/corner4.png\" alt=\"corner4.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n              </td>\n              <td><em>四值語法：</em><code>border-radius: 1em 2em 3em 4em</code> — 這四個值分別代表左上、右上、右下、左下，由左上開始的順時針排序。</td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"背景屬性","title":"背景屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>背景會有下列這些屬性:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>images/bg.gif<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> top right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>可以簡寫為一句宣告：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000 <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>images/bg.gif<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> no-repeat top right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>（寫成簡化屬性的效果，完全等同於上方未簡化的屬性，外加 <code>background-attachment: scroll</code> 及其他 CSS3 中額外增加的屬性。)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"字體屬性","title":"字體屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列的宣告:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> italic<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .8em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>可以簡寫成這樣：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> italic bold .8em/1.2 Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>簡化定義的效果完全等同於未簡化前的屬性效果，加上 <code>font-variant: normal</code>、<code>font-size-adjust: none</code> (CSS2.0 / CSS3) 及 <code>font-stretch: normal</code> (CSS3) 等屬性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"邊框屬性","title":"邊框屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>邊框的寬度、顏色、樣式可以簡寫成一句宣告。舉例來說：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">border-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> solid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>可以寫成：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"邊界與內距屬性","title":"邊界與內距屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>margin 和 padding 的簡化版本大致相同。下列的 CSS 宣告:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">margin-top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin-right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin-bottom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">margin-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>等同於下面的宣告（注意值的排序是順時鐘的順序：上，右，下，左 (TRBL，可以「trouble」這個單字的諧音來記憶）</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px 5px 10px 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相關連結","title":"相關連結","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">CSS Reference (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>Shorthand properties: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background\"><code>background</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/font\"><code>font</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/border\"><code>border</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top\"><code>border-top</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right\"><code>border-right</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom\"><code>border-bottom</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left\"><code>border-left</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-width\"><code>border-width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/border-color\"><code>border-color</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-style\"><code>border-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/transition\"><code>transition</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/transform\"><code>transform</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding\"><code>padding</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/list-style\"><code>list-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-radius\"><code>border-radius</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"定義","id":"定義"},{"text":"需謹慎之處","id":"需謹慎之處"},{"text":"背景屬性","id":"背景屬性"},{"text":"字體屬性","id":"字體屬性"},{"text":"邊框屬性","id":"邊框屬性"},{"text":"邊界與內距屬性","id":"邊界與內距屬性"},{"text":"相關連結","id":"相關連結"}],"summary":"特性簡寫，是一種可以同時設定許多其他 CSS 屬性值的 CSS 屬性。 使用特性簡寫，網頁開發者可以寫出更簡潔、且通常更具可讀性的樣式表，省時又省力。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Shorthand properties","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Propiedades abreviadas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Propriétés raccourcies","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"一括指定プロパティ","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"단축 속성","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Propriedades shorthand","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Краткая форма записи свойств","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS 的简写属性","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/css/shorthand_properties","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/css/shorthand_properties/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties","title":"特性簡寫"}],"pageTitle":"特性簡寫 - CSS | MDN","noIndexing":false}}